The paper deals with the analysis of communication costs in computational DAGs, which is a topic related to distributed computing and graph algorithms. Therefore, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves numerical analysis and optimization, which suggests cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) as a possible sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with the analysis of communication costs in parallel computing, which is related to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SC (Symbolic Computation and Formal Verification).
